What else you need to know:
 Quick Fix comes in a sleek- soft-touch neon green bottle with a frosted white cap. Like other Urban Decay sprays- the sprayer emits a calibrated- micro-fine mist that goes on so light- you’ll hardly feel it—and it and smells like a summer day on the beach.

Research results:
 In a clinical study on 30 people- immediately after use:
- 100% of participants had a reduction in pore visibility
- 100% had a visible improvement in skin radiance
- 83% had a visible improvement in skin hydration
